item.title: CVE-2019-25068|2024-08-05T03:00:19.045Z -- axios%20italia -- axios%20re
item.description: A vulnerability classified as critical was found in Axios Italia Axios RE 1.7.0/7.0.0. This vulnerability affects unknown code of the file REDefault.aspx of the component Connection Handler. The manipulation of the argument DBIDX leads to privilege escalation. The attack can be initiated remotely.

item.title: CVE-2019-25069|2024-08-05T03:00:18.940Z -- axios%20italia -- axios%20re
item.description: A vulnerability, which was classified as problematic, has been found in Axios Italia Axios RE 1.7.0/7.0.0. This issue affects some unknown processing of the component Error Message Handler. The manipulation leads to information disclosure (ASP.NET). The attack may be initiated remotely.
